conversations.conversation:
			We all are explorers on the great sea of life;
<br />;We search and we hunt for our pleasure.
<br />;Some adventures are fruitful, and some disappoint,
<br />;But few find a gem they can treasure.
<br />;<br />;I’m so blessed I found you as my priceless prize;
<br />;You’re a treasure in every way.
<br />;I searched with the rest and discovered the best;
<br />;Finding you was my luckiest day.
